cpu comparison list
as a gener rule of thumb motorola chip ar faster than intel chip at the 
same frequenc {030/25 ~= 386/33; 040/25 ~= 486dx/50}, but intel ha chip at 
higher frequenc than motorola, so thi even out.  the macintosh bibl 4th 
ed. support the comparison between intel and motorola chip for the 68020 
and abov.

<=80186    ~ 68000 {16-bit vs 16/24/32-bit chip [data path/address 
line/data & address regist].  the 4mb limit on the 68000 mac bring it 
down to the 80186 and lower chip, otherwis it would compar to the 80286.}

286        ~ 68020 {hardwar segment vs. 68020's 32-bit alu and these chip 
come have no usabl built-in mmu unlik their successor [80386, 68030].  the 
hardwar segment's protect mode is us by os/2 1.0 => and window 3.x. 
the us of the hardwar segment and their 16-bit natur put the 286 between 
the 60000 and 68030 in featur and the lc's 16-bit data path strenghthen the 
286 ~ 68020 comparison.}

386       ~ 68030 {two 32-bit chip with mmu, and protect memori.  a/ux 3.0 
is at present the onli mac os to us the 68030's protect memori featur for 
app.  system 7.x us thi featur to protect a ram disk creat by the 
memori control panel but thi is support onli on powerbook and quadra.  
the color classic and lcii 16-bit hardwar data path make the 68030s in them 
compar to 386sx.}

486sx   ~ 68lc040 {same as 486 and 68040 without the fpu; us as a low cost 
solut for peopl who do not need the fpu.  onli with program sensit to  
pclk & pipelin doe the 68lc040 behav like 486dx2 - fpu or a '486dx2sx'.}

486     ~ 68040 {two 32-bit microprocessor with built-in fpu, mmu, 8k 
intern cach (which is implement as two 4k cach in the 68040 and on in 
the 486).  onli with program sensit to pclk & pipelin doe the 68040 
behav like a 486dx2.}

pentium   ~ 68060 {both ar plan to be superscalar but both have heat 
problem.  these chip mai flounder against the cheaper (pc week 3/08/93; 
4/12/93; pc mag 4/27/93:110), earlier releas (pc week 12/7/92; macweek 
12/14/92; pc week 2/08/93), less leat produc {160 degre f for pentium
(pc mag 4/27/93:118)}, and partli port to powerpc chip.} 

powerpc   = powerpc {thi cpu line is plan to run program from do, 
window 3.x, os/2 and mac os on top of poweropen-a/ux 4.0 [unix] and later 
pink [talig os] by us emul or, if necessari, the os themselv in 
